    <string name="help_title">Help</string>
    <string name="help_text">
        Welcome to the wallpaper preview and settings page. In the top, you can change preview only
        options - you can customize a light or dark theme and a portrait or landscape mode.
        \n\n
        In the configs below you can change clock\'s position, scale and color. You can even use
        a custom picture as your wallpaper background.
        \n\n
        You can set up clock\'s position and wallpaper image into 2 modes - portrait × landscape.
        For colors on the other hand you have 4 options - portrait × landscape and light × dark mode.
        If you change one mode, your changes WON\'T propagate to any other mode - so make sure
        you have set up all the variants you are actively using. Enjoy!
    </string>
